sellerCard.oneLiner: Wordpress Developer, Certified WIX Specialist, Elementor Designer
sellerCard.description:
My name is Andrew and I am a UK based seller. I am a fully stacked website developer and designer by profession since 2013 where I have adapted and grown with a vast amount of technology. I am a professional seller with excellent communication skills and very good feedback! Contact me for more details on any of my work! 

We work with each one of our clients individually as every individual, business, or brand has its own personality which we ensure we capture so you can showcase your personality across your website to the world.

description.content:
PLEASE CONTACT ME BEFORE ORDERING TO DISCUSS YOUR PROJECT


My name is Andrew and I am verified Certified WIX Velo Developer and I am a WIX Partner on their partner program.


WIX is a great system but sometimes the built in functionality is lacking advanced features. This is where I come into place. I can design, develop and code bespoke custom functionality to really give your website an edge other the overs.


Some examples I offer, but not limited too are:

  • Client Portals
  • Inserting, Updating, Deleting and Selecting data from the Database
  • Custom Login and Signup forms
  • Dynamic Pages
  • and so much more.


Please contact me first to discuss your project to work out the right amount of development time you need for me to code your bespoke functionality.
